name: A ship to Manly
description:
A photograph depicting  a man sitting alone on a boat. "A Ship to Manly", Manly is an Island near Sydney. For this piece "Manly" translates to "Maturity". Maybe some people don't realize that being alone or enjoying solitude is a form of maturity.

Picture was taken in June 2019, Australia. By. @beyond_bjorn aka. Abidzar H.
